      "content": "To project maximum authority, focus on impeccable grooming with clean-shaven faces (or well-groomed beards), neatly trimmed hair, and hands free of distracting jewelry or low-pile cell phones. Dress in dark-colored, high-quality suits with crisp pressed shirts and minimal but coordinated accessories to convey stability and confidence. Maintain strong posture, direct eye contact, and a steady presence throughout the interaction to reinforce your leadership role. Prioritize grooming that looks intentional and polished rather than overly casual or flashy, as this balance is crucial for senior‑level credibility.",
