    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a good start. I'm specifically looking at hair and facial grooming though. For women in these roles, what kind of hairstyles would you recommend to ensure they look \"polished\" and \"intentional\" rather than too casual or distracting during a presentation? I want to make sure we're giving them advice that aligns with that high-authority look.",
